@host = http://localhost:8080
@videoId = 10

### 영상 재생 API - 권한 검증 및 스트리밍 URL 반환
GET {{host}}/api/learning/videos/{{videoId}}/play
Accept: application/json

### 마지막 재생 위치 저장 API
PATCH {{host}}/api/learning/videos/{{videoId}}/progress/position
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "positionSeconds": 142
}
